{
  "stem": "22889.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The ghetto was performed 1941--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--in our town.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We all lived-- of course, my family didn't move together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What happened, we used to trade our homes with our gentile friends.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were already in process to trade our home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then it was a little bit too late already.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was 1942.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So our family-- there were few-- very few family who lived outside the ghetto yet.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because, I mean, our ghetto was open.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't fenced in like in different cities, you know-- the ghetto was fenced in with the wires, and the bricks, and mortar, and stuff like that.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But our ghetto was open.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The only difference was all the Jewish people who lived in this part of the section of the town, the Polish people were there to trade their homes.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had to get out, and the Jewish people were moved in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But you-- if you owned your property, you had a chance to trade in your homes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I don't know about that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They just-- it was a privilege, because we had a little bit more lean than others, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, the mayor in our town, and so forth on--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--they help us in a way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we don't have to-- we won't have to move.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, how can you move?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, you don't want to leave your home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After a while, then those things started.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "September-- no, August the 30-- finally-- I remember the day before-- August the 29.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I came home from my job, from Hobug.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was late at night.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Already it was 10 o'clock, because we used to travel by the train.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had to take the last train-- what was-- and we didn't travel in a regular train.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
